","tid":328938,"uid":62830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但她結識過多位外籍男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個埋佢單慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屎眼都鬆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34cca22831445fcf1f83ebb42829624cf5a1255","tid":328938,"uid":1045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐又指，曾有新娘嫁去外國，<span style=\"color: red;\">母親怕她出嫁後難追家用，一口氣要求女兒給20年家用及禮金</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個老母冇野下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091dbfdfcd40a7d3509ca76990a774e13e9b44ea","tid":328938,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"識玩一定同上海妹結婚"},{"pid":"4333b6e507b263ca0de5093ae9566bb9d63ac1bc","tid":328938,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"咁娶鬼妹洗唔洗比？"},{"pid":"fb9d45839c7c1405f031a842548526b1bfd513c6","tid":328938,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"多位男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公廁唔"},{"pid":"0388356d55a7fd607594fd02a2fbc3eb9e2fde69","tid":328938,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外母係咪當賣女？又俾禮金，但又回返金器。<br />\n唔俾禮金唔回金器咪無事。咩禮金=祝福？我講一句算唔算祝福先</blockquote><br />\n因為老公既錢等於老婆既錢，老婆既錢就係老婆既錢，老公俾禮金外母，外母用禮金買金器俾個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大撚把港女同港女既老母都係咁既心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係鬼佬就係樣樣都分開計，食餐飯都同你aa制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 接受唔到唔好俾個女嫁個洋腸囉<br />\n又要靚基因又要有錢，邊有咁大隻甲乸隨街跳"},{"pid":"33698117aed2532970ec3038c733cedc2ffb8ccc","tid":328938,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n鬼佬就可以貼埋大床<br />\n你試下港男比少個崩都&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03e69b751a6b0e578ed261f481a320f094ee458","tid":328938,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[im<a href=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1860000/1861662/010_01_a_20170720_L.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1860000%2F1861662%2F010_01_a_20170720_L.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=5%2Bt6gKX9MLuhq4I3ofa%2FwbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=7b33385f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1860000/1861662/010_01_a_20170720_L.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n談婚論嫁礙於中西文化有別，要締結異地緣也不易。有女網民指母親思想傳統，明言女兒出嫁一定要收禮金，但她結識過多位外籍男友，但談到結婚時要付禮金都拒絕，為此感為難。有婚禮顧問指，部分新娘會暗地裏自付禮金，減低爭拗機會。<br />\n<br />\n中國傳統婚禮講求禮數，男家給女家禮金，女家也會贈送金器作回禮。有女網民表示媽媽是個傳統中國人，<span style=\"color: red;\">她曾結交多個外籍男友</span>，到了談婚論嫁時，母親硬要收取禮金，而男友都不答應。事主慨嘆<span style=\"color: red;\">：「唔通係香港要遇到個肯畀禮金嘅外籍男友真係咁難？」</span><br />\n<br />\n感對方計較 或致分手收場<br />\n<br />\n有網民笑說「嫁鬼佬要貼埋大床」，又指「嫁鬼佬仲要女家出錢擺酒」。另有人說因人而異，有朋友也是嫁外國人，最後收了20萬禮金。另有人建議女事主私下付禮金，母親會買金器回禮 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁恨嫁洋腸<br />\n但又要人地出禮金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acaae27012581ff46d1e28849f42f6a3f530498","tid":328938,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"講到唔嫁洋腸會死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5e2864e6e8288e915985109585c3f3537f228e","tid":328938,"uid":7458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"係得中國d奇怪婚禮先要比禮金咁on99<br />\n點解要強制人地比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9275e06db4a31a91199d3e227a4bad0be92330b","tid":328938,"uid":58358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係得中國d奇怪婚禮先要比禮金咁on99<br />\n點解要強制人地比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為中國女人中意用個西賺錢<br />\n你依家包起左人地個西咪要一次過畀曬錢先囉"},{"pid":"1666d867c243c509eab562331ed5600279829da5","tid":328938,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你嫁過去，唔係人地入聚，梗係跟人地習俗架啦<br />\n有D地方係女人要俾一大筆嫁妝架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n習俗就要跟？<br />\n你覺得賣女就啱？咁男家家長賣仔咪抵銷返囉"},{"pid":"a0772725023f1ced2c7852b7401733f840e89041","tid":328938,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"遲啲等睇外母叫洋腸女胥肉償&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bb723189282578df77f1efd89f52a03b4eb3e2","tid":328938,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:03:14.000Z","msg":"母親怕她出嫁後難追家用，一口氣要求女兒給20年家用及禮金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260933e341d947940c75f9b0244c243277e1fa64","tid":328938,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11: